    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of high-revving German engineering with this E92 M3. Powered by the S65 4.0L V8 featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline, this unit remains mechanically sharp. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, paired with a limited-slip M Variable Differential for superior lateral dynamics. Crucial preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, has been completed to ensure long-term powertrain integrity. The suspension geometry is tight, and the ventilated braking system retains excellent bite. A well-sorted example for the driver who prioritizes mechanical precision and analog feedback over trailer-queen aesthetics.",
      "price": 34500.0,
