      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been absolute perfection. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape\u2014runs smooth as butter and has been super well-maintained. Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is ready to go with plenty of life left in her. I\u2019ve loved every mile, but it\u2019s time for a new home. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
