    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through its six individual throttle bodies. The high-revving valvetrain remains crisp, with recent VANOS servicing and rod bearing replacement ensuring long-term reliability. Power is transmitted via a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis benefits from reinforced subframe mounting points and a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein B6 dampers, maintaining excellent lateral stability and turn-in response. Dressed in Carbon Black Metallic, the body shows minor road wear consistent with its mileage, while the interior retains its driver-centric ergonomics. A mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s finest naturally aspirated era.",
